name: Warmup_Div04_Sub02
queryText:
SELECT DISTINCT
GmailD4S2.CPF,
GmailD4S2.NOME,
GmailD4S2.EMAIL,
GmailD4S2.EMAIL_VALIDO,
CASE

  WHEN CHARINDEX(' ', GmailD4S2.NOME) = 0 THEN GmailD4S2.NOME

  ELSE SUBSTRING( GmailD4S2.NOME , 1, CHARINDEX(' ', GmailD4S2.NOME) )

END AS PNOME
FROM Gmail_DIV04_SUB02 GmailD4S2
UNION
